      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个云原生应用部署的状态流转图，核心是从HelmChart开始，经过扫描流程，最终可能进入正常状态或者出错。起点是CloudNative_HelmChart，初始状态叫Absent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_HelmChart",
        "Absent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，HelmChart触发初始化进入Absent状态。那扫描动作怎么定义？我看到有Start和End两种扫描事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "Start",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，从Absent出发，如果是Start扫描，就进入CheckedIn状态；但如果是End扫描，而且要关联DockerImage的话，直接进Error状态。然后CheckedIn收到End扫描就转到Attended。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Error",
        "CloudNative_DockerImage",
        "Attended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：Absent到CheckedIn是Start扫描，Absent到Error是End扫描带DockerImage，CheckedIn到Attended是End扫描。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Error",
        "Attended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有两个自循环要注意：CheckedIn状态下如果遇到Start扫描，而且要结合K8sCluster，就保持CheckedIn不变；Attended状态下无论Start还是End扫描，只要涉及ServiceMesh，也是自循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "Attended",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
