      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：CheckedIn的自循环条件是Start扫描加K8sCluster，Attended的自循环是Start或End扫描加ServiceMesh。这两个自循环都画好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后加上错误恢复：Error状态可以通过重置或清理操作回到Absent。另外给Error加个注释，说明这是HelmChart的非法操作导致的。",
      "elements_involved": [
